Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,----------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.71,0:00:08.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恨的伊奥利亚·肖汉博格的亡灵们
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.92,0:00:11.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我亚里桑德罗·科纳
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.74,0:00:16.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来把你们超度到新世界去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.30,0:00:17.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.00,0:00:22.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.87,0:00:23.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.49,0:00:35.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Exia 刹那·F·塞艾
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.18,0:00:36.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始驱逐目标
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.97,0:00:44.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那 瞄准荚仓
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.10,0:00:47.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,运气好的话 能炸了那对钳子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.46,0:00:48.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.75,0:00:54.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干掉了么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.72,0:00:55.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.69,0:00:59.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切 毫发无伤么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.44,0:01:05.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凭那种程度就想对抗Alva Torre
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.16,0:01:06.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可笑之至
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.45,0:02:41.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲露特 告诉我机师们的状况
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.14,0:02:43.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,N…Nadleeh损坏严重
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.83,0:02:46.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提艾利亚…全无应答
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.53,0:02:47.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.95,0:02:50.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kyrios 机体损伤多处
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.44,0:02:52.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与敌方两架MS交战中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.46,0:02:56.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.21,0:03:00.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长翅膀的在卫星群的什么地方躲起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.29,0:03:04.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种机体状况逃不了多远的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.37,0:03:07.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞砸了么 可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.34,0:03:08.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈雷路亚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.29,0:03:09.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.18,0:03:10.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回里面去 阿雷路亚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.75,0:03:14.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没你这生死线上什么都做不到的家伙什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.14,0:03:15.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.11,0:03:17.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算要吸干其他生者的血也会
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.53,0:03:18.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也会活下去的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.69,0:03:19.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.81,0:03:24.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 还没听到世界的回答
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.20,0:03:26.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连这场战斗的意义也…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.80,0:03:28.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在了解到那些之前 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.84,0:03:30.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会死的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.58,0:03:35.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于有那种意思了么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.98,0:03:39.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就去给那女人看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.94,0:03:41.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.16,0:03:42.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「超兵」的模样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.75,0:03:45.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出来了么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.57,0:03:48.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直线攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.85,0:03:50.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,避给你看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.33,0:03:54.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,配合轴线
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.31,0:03:55.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出脚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.08,0:03:56.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并同时攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.70,0:03:59.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.72,0:04:05.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中佐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.89,0:04:13.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,动作不一样了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.50,0:04:15.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那架机体为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.59,0:04:17.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可没功夫像以前那样慢悠悠的!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.93,0:04:19.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对吧 阿雷路亚!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.15,0:04:43.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那武器是和Throne一样的…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.30,0:04:44.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那 连接吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.95,0:04:45.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.47,0:05:08.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GN兵装什么的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.95,0:05:10.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,獠牙!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.35,0:05:13.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,力场展开
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.54,0:05:17.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弹无虚发
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.34,0:05:47.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还真能躲开啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.82,0:05:48.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.86,0:05:54.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冲上去了啊 刹那
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.02,0:05:57.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还真是白痴的老一套
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.61,0:06:04.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么!?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.85,0:06:08.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃这招吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.35,0:06:16.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没完呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.71,0:06:18.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再来一击
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.70,0:06:27.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.11,0:06:29.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将我们的存在…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.42,0:06:33.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉塞
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.12,0:06:35.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这混蛋!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.35,0:06:56.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.54,0:07:17.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能 区区一架Gundam就把我的Alva Torre…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.54,0:07:30.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中佐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.65,0:07:48.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么 我明明是完美的超兵
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.18,0:07:51.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还不清楚啊 女人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.35,0:07:52.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.23,0:07:54.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是完美的超兵
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.48,0:07:58.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然通过脑量子波得到了非同一般的反应能力
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.44,0:08:02.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 你的思想却达不到那种速度
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.50,0:08:05.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是像动物一样遵照本能行动
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.50,0:08:06.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种事情…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.91,0:08:10.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此能看透你的行动
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.48,0:08:13.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反应和思想融合
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.81,0:08:17.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这才是超兵应有的姿态
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.48,0:08:21.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个光辉是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.77,0:08:22.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次的那个么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.81,0:08:23.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.51,0:08:24.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.70,0:08:39.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见了 女人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.23,0:08:41.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.67,0:08:45.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中校
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.26,0:08:47.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是现在 皮瑞斯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.20,0:09:00.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中佐 中佐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.10,0:09:10.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什么 不要管我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.07,0:09:12.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,继续战斗 少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.43,0:09:13.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.87,0:09:16.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中佐如果不在了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.80,0:09:18.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就变成独自一人了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.23,0:09:20.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少尉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.75,0:09:36.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛…玛丽…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.96,0:09:40.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么 为什么是你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.95,0:09:49.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉塞 回答 拉塞
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.59,0:09:52.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.08,0:10:01.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.69,0:10:09.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是拥有原始太阳炉的机体
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.77,0:10:14.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,半吊子的机师就让我这样难堪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.51,0:10:17.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你这家伙吧 扭曲了伊奥利亚的计划
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.61,0:10:19.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,计划还在进行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.15,0:10:23.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是主角换成我了而已
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.36,0:10:27.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 主角就是我 亚里桑德罗·科纳
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.15,0:10:30.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有何企图
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.16,0:10:33.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,破坏与再生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.04,0:10:41.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通过天行者的武力介入 世界被毁灭 并以统一的姿态开始再生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.93,0:10:46.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后 我要把这个世界染上我的颜色
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.30,0:10:49.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要支配一切么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.51,0:10:51.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是引导世界踏上正途啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.87,0:10:56.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 那个新世界里 没有你存在的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.45,0:10:59.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把你轰杀至渣  Exia
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.06,0:11:27.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是遗憾啊 伊奥利亚·肖汉博格
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.06,0:11:31.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,统一世界 引导人类进入新时代的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.22,0:11:35.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我这个现在还活着的人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.74,0:11:39.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什 什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.34,0:11:41.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.25,0:11:43.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Exia
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.69,0:11:45.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊奥利亚的系统么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.44,0:11:46.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.32,0:11:47.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.79,0:11:49.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了 扭曲世界的人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.08,0:11:53.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 你就是元凶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.44,0:11:57.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界的新生已经开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.51,0:12:00.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还要继续破坏下去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.55,0:12:01.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.52,0:12:12.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GN力场
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.24,0:12:19.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那 你知道为什么Exia装备了实体剑吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.11,0:12:22.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是为了与GN力场对抗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.98,0:12:26.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是因为计划中也包括了与Gundam进行的战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.07,0:12:29.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果真到了那时 你就是我们最后的王牌
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.17,0:12:32.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托你了 刹那
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.03,0:12:36.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了 洛克昂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.71,0:12:39.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是一个只会战斗的破坏者
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.46,0:12:43.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以要战斗  为了打倒那些引起纷争的人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.41,0:12:45.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了击碎这个世界的扭曲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.91,0:12:54.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.69,0:12:56.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用武力来根绝战争
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.27,0:13:01.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这才是天行者
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.01,0:13:03.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,力场被…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.69,0:13:05.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam做得到
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.50,0:13:08.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我一起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.85,0:13:11.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 我就是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.81,0:13:18.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们就是Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.29,0:13:25.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里本斯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.77,0:13:27.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亚里桑德罗 科纳
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.55,0:13:29.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真是个不错的小丑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.58,0:13:30.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.99,0:13:33.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是伊奥利亚·肖汉博格的计划
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.24,0:13:36.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是按我的计划进行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.11,0:13:39.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里本斯 混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.56,0:13:43.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界统一的未来就交给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.58,0:13:46.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋 毁了科纳家族的夙愿
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.06,0:13:50.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要这么说的话 还是你自己太弱了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.89,0:13:52.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里本斯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.24,0:14:06.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.31,0:14:13.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Flag 拟造太阳炉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.07,0:14:18.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想与你相会 想与你相会阿 Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.06,0:14:28.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光束剑
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.63,0:14:31.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,霍华德和达里尔的仇 由我来为他们报
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.88,0:14:33.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用这台GN驱动器
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.66,0:14:34.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有通信
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.14,0:14:41.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.67,0:14:43.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是那个时候的少年
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.38,0:14:48.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然你我之前是被命运的红线连在一起的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.82,0:14:52.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 是战斗的命运
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.75,0:14:54.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于理解了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.95,0:15:00.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以压倒性的性能 夺走了我的心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.43,0:15:03.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种感觉 就是爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.21,0:15:05.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.24,0:15:08.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是超越了爱之后 就变成了憎恨
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.44,0:15:13.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像过于执着的信仰也引发了内战
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.27,0:15:17.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然你明白 又为什么要战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.86,0:15:21.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,问军人为什么而战
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.21,0:15:22.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是没有意义的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.29,0:15:27.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已经扭曲了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.90,0:15:30.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,扭曲的是你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.90,0:15:34.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被称为Gundam的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.76,0:15:42.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我要打倒你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.30,0:15:44.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界什么的怎么样都没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.13,0:15:45.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以我的意志
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.89,0:15:49.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你自己本身就是世界的一部分
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.34,0:15:52.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 这就是世界的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.57,0:15:56.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,错了 你只是执着于自我而已
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.98,0:16:00.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的扭曲 就由我来斩断
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.85,0:16:03.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真能说阿 Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.48,0:16:21.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,霍华德 达里尔 你们的仇…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.60,0:16:25.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.15,0:16:46.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能在这里结束
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.03,0:16:51.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,计划还在继续
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.02,0:16:56.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少把太阳炉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.65,0:17:10.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nadleeh放出了GN驱动器
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.61,0:17:12.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提艾利亚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.91,0:17:20.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样终于能来到你的身边 洛克昂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.19,0:17:31.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会 索玛·皮瑞斯居然是玛丽
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.86,0:17:34.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你早知道了吗 哈雷鲁亚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.20,0:17:39.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果知道了的话 你就无法战斗了 只有死路一条
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.88,0:17:48.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 反正是玩笑 我先走一步
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.65,0:17:54.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈雷鲁亚 难道说 怎么会
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.92,0:18:10.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玛丽娜·伊斯玛依露 当你在读这封信的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.38,0:18:12.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经不存于这世上
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.19,0:18:17.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通过武力来根绝战争
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.15,0:18:25.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天行者组织告诉了只会一味战斗的我 战斗的意义所在
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.48,0:18:28.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像当初的Gundam那样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.98,0:18:31.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直渴求着
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.09,0:18:39.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界为什么会如此扭曲 这扭曲又从何而来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.93,0:18:48.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人为什么会抱有无意识的恶意 却又意识不到这股恶意
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.01,0:18:53.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会有那些搅乱人生的事物存在
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.04,0:18:57.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么人们要支配他人 被他人支配
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.36,0:19:00.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要互相伤害
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.57,0:19:06.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便如此 人们又为什么如此想活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.51,0:19:11.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 一直追寻着
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.36,0:19:16.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想只要能与你相见 就一定能获得解答
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.75,0:19:21.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以不同的方式 追寻着同样的事物的你一定能回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.72,0:19:27.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人们能共同前进的道路 这一答案
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.32,0:19:29.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刹那
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.09,0:19:35.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直追寻着 和Gundam一起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.84,0:19:40.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和Gundam一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.82,0:19:49.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露易丝 好久没给你写信了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.63,0:19:55.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自从你没有回信开始 已经过了两年
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.65,0:19:59.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我有件事无论如何想告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.13,0:20:04.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我从今年开始将在宇宙工作
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.10,0:20:07.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然有许多令人悲伤的事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.66,0:20:11.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我实现了这一小小的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.45,0:20:16.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 我想要实现另一个梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.73,0:20:19.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我等着你 露易丝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.96,0:20:21.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在宇宙等着你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.20,0:20:25.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.08,0:20:30.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是GN粒子的光吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.54,0:20:31.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是哪里的机体啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.14,0:20:34.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是联邦的机体
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.19,0:20:36.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,粒子的颜色不对
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.95,0:20:40.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确如此
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.76,0:20:42.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那光…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.48,0:20:45.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 那光是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.40,0:20:46.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.12,0:21:00.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正值国际联合改名为地球联邦一周年之际
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.53,0:21:06.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,经全联邦328个成员国的赞同
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.88,0:21:15.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在此宣布将各国的军队解体 组建一元化的地球联邦维和部队
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.51,0:21:26.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当所有国家的军队不复存在 我们维和部队成为世界唯一军队之时
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.04,0:21:31.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界将获得真正的统一
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.52,0:21:36.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们将以此为道标 稳步前进
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.50,0:21:40.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话 世界算是改变了吧 小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.91,0:21:44.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁知道 你对现在的世界不满意吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.24,0:21:49.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有所期待 对世界的改变
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.98,0:21:57.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要开始了 革新 人类的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.92,0:22:26.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,劳您大驾了 小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.21,0:22:27.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情况如何
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.13,0:22:29.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一架已经出产了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.83,0:22:32.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在在做实战准备的测试
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.86,0:22:34.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其它的机体呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.19,0:22:37.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,按计划将依次出产
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.49,0:22:39.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,方便的话能让我观摩一下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.80,0:22:41.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一代的机体
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.20,0:22:43.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.65,0:23:03.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是0 Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.12,0:23:07.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一台搭载太阳炉运作的机体
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.77,0:23:11.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已将卸下的太阳炉组装上了机体
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.85,0:23:14.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但就算这个也不匹配
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.67,0:23:20.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算用Exia的太阳炉也不知能否顺利运作
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.20,0:23:29.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,改变世界的机体 00 Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.96,0:17:57.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈雷鲁亚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.85,0:10:34.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,--------
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.84,0:21:10.55,Last,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}ねえ　こんな形の出逢いしか　なかったの？　悲しいね
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.30,0:21:22.85,Last,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}あなたに　死んでも殺めて　欲しくも無い　お願い
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.78,0:21:34.62,Last,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}運命さえ飲み込まれ　沈みそうな　海へと
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.25,0:21:44.81,Last,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}願いよ風に乗って　夜明けの鐘を鳴らせよ　鳥のように
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.81,0:21:47.58,Last,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}my wishes over their airspace
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.58,0:21:57.09,Last,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}無数の波を超え　明日へ立ち向かうあなたを　守りたまえ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.09,0:21:59.79,Last,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}my life I trade in for your pain
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.79,0:22:05.24,Last,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}振り向かず羽ばたけ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.75,0:22:12.33,Last,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}この想いを運んで　あの空を飛んでく
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.61,0:22:19.44,Last,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,600)}未来は誰にも　撃ち落とせない
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.84,0:21:10.55,Lastcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}呐 除了这样的相见 别无他法么? 悲伤 彻骨
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.30,0:21:22.85,Lastcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}你 即使我堕入地狱 也不愿伤害 希望 绝望
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.78,0:21:34.62,Lastcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}命运也被点点啃噬 堕向那绝望的深海
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.25,0:21:44.81,Lastcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}愿望啊愿望请乘上疾风 去敲响破晓的钟 如飞鸟一般
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.58,0:21:57.09,Lastcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}超越吧超越那无数风浪 向明日抗争的你 请替我守护
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.79,0:22:05.24,Lastcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}莫再回首 振翅去飞
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.75,0:22:12.33,Lastcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)}请带着请带着这份思念 飞到那一片天空
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.61,0:22:19.44,Lastcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,600)}那是谁都不能击落的未来


